<h1 class="py-2 h1">Import</h1>
<p class="py-2">Command exports 8 components.</p>

<ExportItem title="Root">Wraps command palette state.</ExportItem>
<ExportItem title="Trigger">Opens the command palette.</ExportItem>
<ExportItem title="Content">Modal surface for the palette.</ExportItem>
<ExportItem title="Search">Input used to filter commands.</ExportItem>
<ExportItem title="Results">Container for visible command items.</ExportItem>
<ExportItem title="Group">Optional labeled grouping for related items.</ExportItem>
<ExportItem title="Item">Single command action.</ExportItem>
<ExportItem title="Separator">Visual divider between command groups.</ExportItem>

<h1 class="py-6 h1">Example</h1>

